WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.220
Cheers!

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.500
The youth from all over Japan are gathered here.

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:35.500
They are different from each other.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.500
But as friends who love the same God,

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:40.000
they pray together,

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.000
pray together,

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.000
chat together,

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.000
and laugh together.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.500
God will create a new connection.

00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.500
In the camp,

00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:49.500
Japanese, Korean, English,

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:51.500
three languages are together.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:54.500
And in the small group discussion,

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:58.000
we discuss how to grow in faith with friends.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.000
There are lots of games,

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:01.000
activities,

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.000
and campfires at night.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.000
There are so many great programs.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:10.000
We have the best location with a view of Mt. Fuji.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.000
In a nature retreat setting,

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:17.000
a little distance from our everyday lives,

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
we meet friends with a shared heart.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
It's not just a fun camp —

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:26.000
a new way of life with a new dream will begin.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:38.000
From August 4th to 6th, 2026,
this summer, experience something new that God will begin.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.000
We are looking forward to your participation!
